Package edu.ntnu.idatt1002.team20.models.expense

Class Expense

java.lang.Object
edu.ntnu.idatt1002.team20.models.expense.Expense
public class Expense extends Object
Class for expense. Represents an expense with a source, amount, deadline and linked debt or goal. Methods for manipulating the expenses values and getting the linked debt or goal (or both).
